data.description: Custom one owner, ranch home, first time offered on the market. This home sits on a beautiful 6+ acres with a portion of it wooded. Home offers entry area to formal dining room or an office. Family room, eat-in kitchen combined to make a 16'x39' open area. Kitchen offers custom maple cabinets, Corian countertops, plentiful cabinets with abundance of countertop space including island with bar stool area and glass door leading to an oversized back deck overlooking your spacious back yard. Master suite offers full bathroom and has a 7'x6' walk-in closet.  2nd full bath offers a walk-in shower and two additional spacious bedrooms. Upstairs offers plentiful closets space, including pantry area. Laundry room off kitchen leads to garage with an oversized space of 12'x21' for workshop or additional parking space and heated. Lower level offers an additional 2100 sq ft of space ready to be finished into additional bedrooms, rec room and includes French doors to lower level patio to the back yard. Lower level offers a finished full bath. Outdoor wood burner and home also set up to run off of propane heat, two water heaters, 3' interior doors, central vacuum throughout home, floor joist trusses, outdoor shed and so much more.   This home has been meticulously maintained and cared for, ready for its new​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ owner.
